  "detailed_description": "Ancient alien monuments are scattered across the universe like drops of werkle flung from the end of Sopsabble’s flobber… no, like psychedelic raisins dotted all the way through a Datrippian spacecake… no, no, like exquisite treasures in an Opudumm mine! The point is, there are loads of them. And they are the key to ruling the stars themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.poster.avif?t=1726187877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.webm?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.mp4?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build spaceships planetside and launch skywards - conquer enemy territory and race to be the first to reactivate derelict monuments. Activate the monuments in each sector to control your constellation. When you control the constellations, you control the galaxy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.poster.avif?t=1726187877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.webm?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.mp4?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Will you battle as the tough, street-smart Sasharkpas? The madcap-genius Fringlots? Or the efficient, no-nonsense Practwomms? Unlock even more diverse alien factions with unique abilities as you progress through the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/23951b8a4eca7027b943a2afb96911de.poster.avif?t=1726187877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/23951b8a4eca7027b943a2afb96911de.webm?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/23951b8a4eca7027b943a2afb96911de.mp4?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/e56f6efceff9525eadd8e0f2efdb0fc4.avif?t=1726187877\" width=511 height=310 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/89b7d566d6b634d2e9c384a391b82f13.avif?t=1726187877\" width=555 height=151 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Ancient alien monuments are scattered across the universe like drops of werkle flung from the end of Sopsabble’s flobber… no, like psychedelic raisins dotted all the way through a Datrippian spacecake… no, no, like exquisite treasures in an Opudumm mine! The point is, there are loads of them. And they are the key to ruling the stars themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.poster.avif?t=1726187877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.webm?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/defb7dde1a93228d71cb0be1f7f568e4.mp4?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build spaceships planetside and launch skywards - conquer enemy territory and race to be the first to reactivate derelict monuments. Activate the monuments in each sector to control your constellation. When you control the constellations, you control the galaxy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.poster.avif?t=1726187877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.webm?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073490/extras/6765b29fe3707f30d7f6161fac28a75e.mp4?t=1726187877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Will you battle as the tough, street-smart Sasharkpas? The madcap-genius Fringlots? Or the efficient,